## 🔄 Updating Guidelines
- **Automatic Sync**: Any new `page.tsx` in `src/app` must be automatically reflected in `llms.txt`, `llms-full.txt`, and the dynamic `sitemap.xml`.
- **Internal Linking**: No page should exist as an "island." Every vertical must link back to the Persona hubs and the Feature pillars.